# dotnet.calcifer — Site Map & Technical Architecture

> A secure .NET 8 Web API template with JWT authentication, ASP.NET Identity, and role-based authorization.
> **Author:** Rakibul | **Database:** SQL Server | **API Docs:** Swagger/OpenAPI

---

