## 🌐 API Endpoint Map (Site Map)

### MVC Controllers (`MapControllers`)

| Method | Route | Controller | Auth | Description |
|--------|-------|------------|------|-------------|
| `POST` | `/api/v1/Auth/register` | [AuthController](file:///d:/alpha/dotnet/dotnet.calcifer/src/Calcifer.Api/v1/Controllers/AuthController/AuthController.cs#12-52) | 🔓 Open | Register a new user account |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/Auth/login` | [AuthController](file:///d:/alpha/dotnet/dotnet.calcifer/src/Calcifer.Api/v1/Controllers/AuthController/AuthController.cs#12-52) | 🔓 Open | Login & receive JWT token |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/Auth/logout` | [AuthController](file:///d:/alpha/dotnet/dotnet.calcifer/src/Calcifer.Api/v1/Controllers/AuthController/AuthController.cs#12-52) | 🔒 Bearer | Sign out current user |
| `POST` | `/api/Role/create` | [RoleController](file:///d:/alpha/dotnet/dotnet.calcifer/src/Calcifer.Api/v1/Controllers/AuthController/RoleController.cs#9-35) | 🔓 Open* | Create a new role |
| `POST` | `/api/Role/assign` | [RoleController](file:///d:/alpha/dotnet/dotnet.calcifer/src/Calcifer.Api/v1/Controllers/AuthController/RoleController.cs#9-35) | 🔓 Open* | Assign role to a user |
| `GET`  | `/` | [HomeController](file:///d:/alpha/dotnet/dotnet.calcifer/src/Calcifer.Api/v1/Controllers/HomeController.cs#13-45) | 🔒 Bearer | Get public data |

> \* [RoleController](file:///d:/alpha/dotnet/dotnet.calcifer/src/Calcifer.Api/v1/Controllers/AuthController/RoleController.cs#9-35) has `[Authorize(Roles = "Admin")]` **commented out** — currently open.

### Minimal APIs ([ApplicationMinimalApis](file:///d:/alpha/dotnet/dotnet.calcifer/src/Calcifer.Api/v1/Middleware/MiddlewareDependencyInversion.cs#20-54))

All minimal API endpoints are grouped under `/api/v1` with the [AuthorizationFilter](file:///d:/alpha/dotnet/dotnet.calcifer/src/Calcifer.Api/v1/AuthHandler/Filters/AuthorizationFilter.cs#9-30) applied:

| Method | Route | Group | Auth | Description |
|--------|-------|-------|------|-------------|
| `GET` | `/api/v1/identity/identity/user/{id}` | Identity | 🔒 AdminPolicy | Get user by ID |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/identity/identity/roles/{id}` | Identity | 🔒 Bearer | Get roles for user |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/public/` | Public | 🔒 Filter | Get public data |

