## 🏗️ Architecture & Developer Interaction System

### Layered Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph Client["🖥️ Client (Frontend)"]
        FE["Vue 3 + Pinia<br/>localhost:5173"]
    end

    subgraph Pipeline["ASP.NET Middleware Pipeline"]
        CORS["CORS Policy"]
        AUTH["UseAuthentication"]
        AUTHZ["UseAuthorization"]
    end

    subgraph Endpoints["API Endpoints"]
        MVC["MVC Controllers<br/>(AuthController, RoleController, HomeController)"]
        MIN["Minimal APIs<br/>(IdentityApi, PublicCRUDApis)"]
    end

    subgraph Services["Business Logic"]
        AS["AuthService"]
        RS["RoleService"]
        TS["TokenService"]
        PS["PublicService"]
    end

    subgraph Data["Data Layer"]
        CTX["CalciferAppDbContext<br/>(IdentityDbContext)"]
        SQL["SQL Server<br/>CalciferDB"]
    end

    FE -->|HTTP + JWT| CORS --> AUTH --> AUTHZ
    AUTHZ --> MVC
    AUTHZ --> MIN
    MVC --> AS & RS & PS
    MIN --> PS
    AS --> TS
    AS & RS --> CTX
    CTX --> SQL
```

### Authentication & Authorization Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant Auth as AuthController
    participant Svc as AuthService
    participant Token as TokenService
    participant DB as SQL Server

    C->>API: POST /api/v1/Auth/register
    API->>Auth: RegisterRequestDto
    Auth->>Svc: RegisterAsync(dto)
    Svc->>DB: UserManager.CreateAsync()
    Svc->>Token: GenerateJwtToken(user)
    Token->>DB: GetRolesAsync(user)
    Token-->>Svc: JWT string
    Svc-->>Auth: (true, token, null)
    Auth-->>C: 200 { access_token }

    C->>API: POST /api/v1/Auth/login
    API->>Auth: LoginRequestDto
    Auth->>Svc: LoginAsync(email, password)
    Svc->>DB: FindByEmailAsync + PasswordSignIn
    Svc->>Token: GenerateJwtToken(user)
    Token-->>Svc: JWT string
    Svc-->>Auth: (true, token, "")
    Auth-->>C: 200 { access_token }

    C->>API: GET /api/v1/public/ (Bearer token)
    API->>API: Validate JWT (Issuer, Audience, Signing Key)
    API->>API: AuthorizationFilter check
    API-->>C: 200 { status, message, data }
```

