## ⚙️ Technology Stack

| Layer | Technology | Version |
|-------|-----------|---------|
| **Runtime** | .NET | 8.0 |
| **Framework** | ASP.NET Core Web API | 8.0 |
| **Authentication** | JWT Bearer (HMAC-SHA256) | 8.0.1 |
| **Identity** | ASP.NET Core Identity | 8.0.1 |
| **ORM** | Entity Framework Core | 8.0.1 |
| **Database** | SQL Server (LocalDB/Express) | — |
| **API Docs** | Swashbuckle (Swagger) | 6.4.0 |
| **API Patterns** | MVC Controllers + Minimal APIs | Hybrid |
| **Frontend (CORS)** | Vue 3 @ `localhost:5173` | — |

