## 🔧 Developer Interaction System (DI & Config)

### Dependency Injection Registration

All services are registered in [DependencyInversion.cs](file:///d:/alpha/dotnet/dotnet.calcifer/src/Calcifer.Api/v1/DependencyContainer/DependencyInversion.cs):

| Registration | Lifetime | Purpose |
|-------------|----------|---------|
| [IPublicInterface](file:///d:/alpha/dotnet/dotnet.calcifer/src/Calcifer.Api/v1/Interface/Common/IPublicInterface.cs#3-8) → [PublicService](file:///d:/alpha/dotnet/dotnet.calcifer/src/Calcifer.Api/v1/Services/PublicService.cs#8-15) | Scoped | Public data abstraction |
| [TokenService](file:///d:/alpha/dotnet/dotnet.calcifer/src/Calcifer.Api/v1/Services/AuthService/TokenService.cs#12-49) | Scoped | JWT token generation |
| [AuthService](file:///d:/alpha/dotnet/dotnet.calcifer/src/Calcifer.Api/v1/Services/AuthService/AuthService.cs#9-79) | Scoped | Register & login logic |
| `Identity<ApplicationUser, ApplicationRole>` | (Identity defaults) | User + role management |
| [CalciferAppDbContext](file:///d:/alpha/dotnet/dotnet.calcifer/src/Calcifer.Api/v1/DbContexts/CalciferAppDbContext.cs#11-35) | Scoped | EF Core database context |
| [JwtSettings](file:///d:/alpha/dotnet/dotnet.calcifer/src/Calcifer.Api/v1/AuthHandler/Configuration/JwtSettings.cs#3-10) | Singleton (Options) | JWT configuration binding |
| `IHttpContextAccessor` | Singleton | HTTP context access |

### Authorization Policies

| Policy | Requirement |
|--------|------------|
| `AdminPolicy` | Role = "Admin" |
| `ManagerPolicy` | Role = "Manager" |
| `OfficerPolicy` | Role = "Officer" |

### JWT Token Claims

| Claim | Source |
|-------|--------|
| `ID` | `ApplicationUser.Id` |
| `Name` | `ApplicationUser.UserName` |
| `Email` | `ApplicationUser.Email` |
| `role` (multiple) | `UserManager.GetRolesAsync()` |

### Configuration ([appsettings.json](file:///d:/alpha/dotnet/dotnet.calcifer/src/Calcifer.Api/appsettings.json))

| Key | Value |
|-----|-------|
| `ConnectionStrings:CalciferDBContext` | `Server=localhost;Database=CalciferDB;...` |
| `JwtSettings:Issuer` | `calcifer.api` |
| `JwtSettings:Audience` | `calcifer.client` |
| `JwtSettings:ExpirationInMinutes` | `60` |

