## 🗄️ Database Schema (Entity Models)

### [ApplicationUser](file:///d:/alpha/dotnet/dotnet.calcifer/src/Calcifer.Api/v1/DbContexts/AuthModels/ApplicationUser.cs#7-25) (extends `IdentityUser`)

| Field | Type | Notes |
|-------|------|-------|
| `AppUserGuid` | `Guid` | Auto-generated |
| `EmployeeId` | `string(50)` | Required, unique index |
| `Name` | `string` | Display name |
| `Region` | `string?` | Optional |
| [Status](file:///d:/alpha/dotnet/dotnet.calcifer/src/Calcifer.Api/v1/DTOs/CommonDTO/CommonStatusDto.cs#3-12) | `int` | Active/Inactive |
| `CreatedAt` / `UpdatedAt` | `DateTime?` | Timestamps |
| `CreateAt` / `UpdateAt` / `DeleteAt` | `DateTime` | Audit dates |
| `UpdateBy` / `DeleteBy` | `string?` | Audit actors |
| `IsDeleted` | `bool` | Soft delete flag |

### [ApplicationRole](file:///d:/alpha/dotnet/dotnet.calcifer/src/Calcifer.Api/v1/DbContexts/AuthModels/ApplicationRole.cs#5-10) (extends `IdentityRole`)

| Field | Type |
|-------|------|
| `Description` | `string?` |
| [Status](file:///d:/alpha/dotnet/dotnet.calcifer/src/Calcifer.Api/v1/DTOs/CommonDTO/CommonStatusDto.cs#3-12) | `int?` |

### [PublicData](file:///d:/alpha/dotnet/dotnet.calcifer/src/Calcifer.Api/v1/DbContexts/Models/PublicData.cs#5-12)

| Field | Type |
|-------|------|
| `Guid` (PK) | `Guid` |
| `Name` | `string` |
| `Description` | `string?` |

### [TableOperationDetails](file:///d:/alpha/dotnet/dotnet.calcifer/src/Calcifer.Api/v1/DbContexts/Common/TableOperationDetails.cs#3-16) (base class, not mapped)

| Field | Type | Notes |
|-------|------|-------|
| `StatusId` | `int` | Status flag |
| `CreatedBy` / `UpdatedBy` / `DeletedBy` | `string?` | Audit actors |
| `CreatedAt` | `DateTime` | Default UTC+6 |
| `UpdatedAt` / `DeletedAt` | `DateTime?` | — |
| `IsDeleted` | `bool` | Soft delete |

